public class ScatteredAssetAccessTemplate
extends MappedAssetAccessTemplate<ScatteredAsset>

This class provides simple access to AssetData. It is intended to be a one-stop-shop for all read operations on assets.

In many cases it returns a ScatteredAsset for easy access to AssetData.

The object has the same lifecycle as the ICS object, one per request.

Author:
Dolf Dijkstra
